    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/d8718080c8a5b7c083f4aac56b846c99.poster.avif?t=1734112838\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/d8718080c8a5b7c083f4aac56b846c99.webm?t=1734112838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/d8718080c8a5b7c083f4aac56b846c99.mp4?t=1734112838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been hired by a mysterious truck driver with one simple mission: assemble your team, venture into eerie, abandoned locations, and gather enough valuable loot to meet up to three cash quotas before the clock runs out. In this online co-op survival horror experience, failure means no payday, and every decision counts as you race against the clock to scavenge, survive, and cash out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll have to use a range of tools to navigate crumbling structures and dark corridors, but stay alert—danger lurks in every shadow. As you explore, you’ll encounter unpredictable threats, from environmental hazards to hostile forces that will stop at nothing to keep you from your prize. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay together, strategize carefully, and keep an eye on the clock. Will you meet the quota, or end up empty-handed?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/680e3a3cac9bf3bd53ced23e2457beb4.poster.avif?t=1734112838\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/680e3a3cac9bf3bd53ced23e2457beb4.webm?t=1734112838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/680e3a3cac9bf3bd53ced23e2457beb4.mp4?t=1734112838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>[</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BRING YOUR TOOLS AND FRIENDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have friends who could use some extra money, they are welcome to join the crew. The more people you have, the faster you can complete the task, which will reduce the risk of accidents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During the job, it's very important to use the proper tools and equipment, which you can purchase from the truck with the wages you've earned by then. Of course, you'll need to provide your own basic protective gear, as the driver won't take responsibility for any injuries.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/b16082d32b2e80ecd5d446079181a828.poster.avif?t=1734112838\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/b16082d32b2e80ecd5d446079181a828.webm?t=1734112838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/b16082d32b2e80ecd5d446079181a828.mp4?t=1734112838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE TRUCK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equipped with the latest groundbreaking technologies, the team’s truck is one of the most advanced mobile work centers today. It features a tool shop, a dedicated company intranet hub, a computer network necessary for job assignments, a first aid kit (currently empty but in the process of being restocked), as well as lockers for storing clothing and protective gear. To the driver, the comfort of the workers is just as important as their safety and health!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/98d82220c92305767f29c159b30ed04c.poster.avif?t=1734112838\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/98d82220c92305767f29c159b30ed04c.webm?t=1734112838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252400/extras/98d82220c92305767f29c159b30ed04c.mp4?t=1734112838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
